@startuml
title Build Process Workflow (Corrected)

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #ADD8E6
  BorderColor #4682B4
  ArrowColor #4682B4
}

[*] --> Clean
[*] --> Setup

state "Setup" as Setup {
  state Prepare
  state Restore
  state Versioning

  Prepare --> Restore
  Prepare --> Versioning
}

' All setup tasks and Clean must complete before Compile
Clean --> Compile
Setup --> Compile

state "Testing (Optional)" as Testing {
  state UnitTest
  state UITest
  state Coverage

  Compile --> UnitTest
  Compile --> UITest
  UnitTest --> Coverage
  UITest --> Coverage
}

note top of Testing : Not on the default execution path

Compile --> Publish
Publish --> Pack

Pack --> [*]

' Separate Analysis Flow
' Analyze depends on Restore, which is part of the Setup group.
Setup --> Analyze
Analyze --> [*]

note right of Pack
  The default target is **Pack**.
  This diagram shows the main
  execution path and dependencies
  required to create the final artifacts.
end note

note left of Analyze
  **Analyze** is a separate target
  that can be run after Restore
  for static code analysis.
end note
@enduml